RACE.RACE_TEXT: CANTERBURY PARK RACE 1 6 1/2F Dirt CR: 81. Claiming Purse 18500. FOR FILLIES AND MARES THREE YEARS OLD AND UPWARD WHICH HAVE NEVER WON THREE RACES OR MINNESOTA BRED WHICH HAVE NEVER WON FOUR RACES OR WHICH HAVE NOT WON A RACE SINCE AUGUST 3, 2022. Three Year Olds, 119 lbs.; Older, 124 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Since July 3 Allowed 2 lbs. Claiming Price $20,000. Minnesota Bred Claiming Price $30,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: FREEBRITNEY set the pressured pace while racing two-wide, shook off TAKING CHARGE DESI entering the stretch and was ridden out to increase her advantage. O'BABE was prominent early while racing along the inside, dropped back slightly on the turn, angled out to come three-wide into the stretch and finished in a mild rally. TAKING CHARGE DESI broke in to bump with ARTISTIC VISION, then prompted FREEBRITNEY from along the inside to the stretch and weakened slightly late. ARTISTIC VISION broke out to bump with TAKE CHARGE DESI, then was forwardly placed, moved up three-wide to offer her bid nearing the quarter pole and then faltered during the drive.

CHEST CANDY was forwardly place early while racing three-wide and weakened during the drive. PUSH THROUGH chased the pace from along the inside for a half mile and gave way.
